s/releasing.md.\n\n## Scope\nShip the 51 commits on origin/main since v0.9.1 as a minor release (new features present: reconciler Backend port + config, capability-tiered model delegation, ChatGPT connector guide, phased plan-review attestations, plus fixes incl. runner-metadata prerequisite payload fix 60a0eab88).\n\n## Plan\n1. Bump versions in lockstep: pyproject.toml, server.json (top-level + packages[].version), CHANGELOG.md ([Unreleased]->[0.10.0]).\n2. Local gates: make lint && make typecheck && make test; python -m build && twine check dist/*.\n3. Land the bump commit through Gerrit (LLM-Review +1 AND Verified +1), then Submit.\n4. Dispatch release.yml from main (version=0.10.0); approve pypi deployment.\n5. Verify all channels: PyPI live, Homebrew autobump, MCP Registry, GitHub Release.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- v0.10.0 published to PyPI (nava-rebar==0.10.0 installs).\n- version-lockstep across pyproject.toml/server.json passes the release authorize gate.\n- CHANGELOG.md has a curated [0.10.0] section.\n- GitHub Release v0.10.0 created (Latest, artifacts attached); MCP Registry shows 0.10.0; Homebrew formula bumped.","env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","file_impact":[{"path":"pyproject.toml","reason":"version bump 0.9.1->0.10.0"},{"path":"server.json","reason":"version bump (top-level + packages[].version)"},{"path":"CHANGELOG.md","reason":"promote unreleased -> [0.10.0] section"}],"keyring":[],"last_status_env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","managed_refs":[],"parent_id":null,"parent_status_uuid":"872d3657-6c0f-4184-9d10-f2297a080fc0","plan_review_phase":"execution","preconditions_summary":{"status":"pre-manifest"},"priority":2,"reverts":[],"status":"in_progress","tags":[],"ticket_id":"307a-40db-3537-4e1f","ticket_type":"task","title":"Release v0.10.0 — minor release from origin/main","verify_commands":[]},"source_event_uuids":["0f309960-796e-4782-93ff-ee808d1a7e06","355e9264-9913-433b-9a5f-51ef1824ae67","29383154-4ab8-4ea6-93b4-0